ProvisionedIops.description:
The provisioned read/write IOPS of the ESSD AutoPL disk to use as the system disk. Valid values: 0 to min{50,000, 1,000 × Capacity - Baseline IOPS}.

Baseline performance = min{1,800 + 50 × Capacity, 50,000}

This parameter is available only if you set `DiskCategory` to `cloud_auto`. For more information, see [ESSD AutoPL disks](~~368372~~).

ExtraAttributes.description:
Extra attributes of event, possible fields are:

- EcsInstanceId: ECS instance ID where the cloud disk is mounted;
- Adapter: cloud disk mount point.
